South Africa's Bafana Bafana beat Zimbabwe 2-0 in a 2002 World
Cup qualifying match which was abandoned in the 82nd minute.
</P>
<P>
Pandemonium broke out when the police fired teargas to quell
hooligans who were throwing missiles on the pitch. 
