weapons and transporting drugs will continue fully vehement
because that is where the drug trafficker makes highest earnings".
</P>
<P>
He said that the weapons guerrillas receive are made in
European countries, especially Russia and "arrive to foment
violence in Colombia".
</P>
<P>
The Minister asked the international community to make greater
efforts to control sending of arms and chemical precursors for
narcotic processing.
</P>
<P>
Control of weapon and chemical prcursor exports is a
fundamental strategy for success of "Plan Colombia", with which
President Andres Pastrana intends development, peace and drug
fighting in the country, he added.  
