</P>
<P>
The royal entourage include Foreign Minister Josep Pique and
Education Minister Pilar del Castillo.
</P>
<P>
The Spanish Foreign Minister will hold talks with his Brazilian
counterpart Paulo Renato Souza in order to discuss a project to
make obligatory the teaching of Spanish in Brazilian secondary
education.
</P>
<P>
Spain is its second largest foreign investor, following the
United States.
</P>
</TEXT>
