many fields such as science and technology, education as well as
culture. The bilateral ties will be certain to have greater
advance under the concerted efforts made by both the Chinese and
Belgian governments and the king's care and concern, Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese Premier today also attended a luncheon hosted by
Belgian Prince Philips. He expressed his appreciation for the
prince's contribution to the development of Sino-Belgian relations.
</P>
