the ARF meeting to promote reconciliation with countries which do
not have diplomatic ties with Pyongyang.
</P>
<P>
South Korea, prompted by a landmark inter-Korean summit last
month, has promised to support DPRK joining the ARF, an
organization that groups 22 Southeast and Northeast Asian nations.
</P>
<P>
It was reported that DPRK's entry of ARF will be one of the
major agenda at the meeting. 
