The new benchmark S&AMP;P/ASX200 gained 18.5 points to a new record
high of 3323.8 points. The all ordinaries index added 18.9 points
to a new record high of 3279.9 points.
</P>
<P>
National turnover was 688.76 million shares at a value of 1.26
billion Australian dollars (748.94 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
