State for non-proliferation, and the DPRK delegation is headed by
Jang Chang Chon, director-general for US affairs at the foreign
ministry. The scheduled three-day meeting is being held at the US
embassy here and is expected to cover a wide range of issues,
including US concerns over DPRK's missiles programs. (Malaysia-US-
DPRK-Talks)
