people in violence-torn areas repair their house will remain
unchanged.
</P>
<P>
She said her office is making efforts to help the people whose
houses were destroyed during the riots or natural disasters get
access to banking credits.
</P>
<P>
The Dutch government recently donated 3.5 million U.S. dollars
to help rebuild houses in riot-torn areas and in Bengkulu province,
which was hit by a devastating earthquake on June 4.
</P>
<P>
